{"tid":2304170,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"置業人士踴躍入市，施政報告對樓市影響正面","createTime":"2020-11-28T14:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T14:21:21.000Z","uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"90fd80bd2b87debd4b809afa213cd7a91eae3d6d","tid":2304170,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T14:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ZV9iuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ZV9iuf.jpg&h=483d453f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大圍站柏傲莊II昨進行第四輪銷售315伙， 消息指，截至昨晚7時半，單日沽出275伙，銷售率87.3%，套現逾32億元。其他新盤亦各錄逾十倍入票，油塘蔚藍東岸周六開售首輪279伙，昨晚截收逾4,000票，超額認購13倍；今晚開售首輪68伙的尖沙咀本木昨截收1,137票，超額認購15.7倍。發展商指出，置業人士踴躍入市，反映施政報告措施對樓市影響正面<br />\n<br />\n疫苗即將推出，預計明年下半年樓市會有報復性反彈。"},{"pid":"4c5cf1a110bd00adefa99100b27069f17b2937c0","tid":2304170,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T14:06:04.000Z","msg":"又係假新聞？"},{"pid":"8805584b9b07a435c31306e5e193972aee61c0ba","tid":2304170,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4c5cf1a110bd00adefa99100b27069f17b2937c0","tid":2304170,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T14:06:04.000Z","msg":"又係假新聞？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T14:15:00.000Z","msg":"呢一兩年不嬲得新盤清<br />\n二手靜過鬼，二房叫好少少<br />\n豪宅要蝕讓<br />\n新盤都唔可以1q清就玩完啦"},{"pid":"415f9fdb46b7366b89a02b5dcd6e4d79efd78051","tid":2304170,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8805584b9b07a435c31306e5e193972aee61c0ba","tid":2304170,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4c5cf1a110bd00adefa99100b27069f17b2937c0","tid":2304170,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T14:06:04.000Z","msg":"又係假新聞？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T14:15:00.000Z","msg":"呢一兩年不嬲得新盤清<br />\n二手靜過鬼，二房叫好少少<br />\n豪宅要蝕讓<br />\n新盤都唔可以1q清就玩完啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T14:21:21.000Z","msg":"多數2q清wow"}]}